            <h2>Welcome to Adopt A Cat/Dog</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Adopt A Cat/Dog, your one-stop destination for finding a loving home for your furry friend or adopting a new pet. We are dedicated to connecting loving families with cats and dogs in need of a home.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to ensure that every pet finds a loving and caring family. We have a wide variety of cats and dogs looking for homes, and we strive to make the adoption process as smooth and stress-free as possible.</p>
            <p>Whether you are looking to adopt a pet or need to find a new home for your pet, we are here to help. Explore our website to learn more about our available pets, pet care tips, and how you can get involved in our mission.</p>
